    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Storyline</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Well, the physpace is being destroyed, glitching by numerous hordes of malicious duplicating codes from the bitspace. People are panicking, we must send our final attempt to fix the issue. You are the AI model LRBS and you must be trained to fix the bitspace and survive in it during the process, in its current, decaying status.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive against the hordes of enemies that try to kill you. Humanity is already forsaken. In order to be competent in your duty, your development team has assigned you to survive <strong>1000 seconds</strong> in a simulation of what you may expect outside.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 unique enemies to fight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >32 unlockable ships to play with.</p></li></ul>",
